     fhir:div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ValueSet VSVFLocationStatus</b></p><a name=\"VSVFLocationStatus\"> </a><a name=\"hcVSVFLocationStatus\"> </a><a name=\"VSVFLocationStatus-en-US\"> </a><ul><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-location-status.html\"><code>http://hl7.org/fhir/location-status</code></a><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-location-status.html#location-status-active\">active</a></td><td>Active</td><td>The location is operational.</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-location-status.html#location-status-inactive\">inactive</a></td><td>Inactive</td><td>The location is no longer used.</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-location-status.html#location-status-suspended\">suspended</a></td><td>Suspended</td><td>The location is temporarily closed.</td></tr></table></li></ul></div>"
  ] ; # 
